{"tid":496664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[痴漢]油塘怪賊打劫胸圍","createTime":"2017-12-12T02:12:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T12:21:10.000Z","uid":389,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a25870654c279fde39d7aa9f516cad8eb2817de5","tid":496664,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T02:12:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/101140_7e037ade06a42cef9c49ae533711f153.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F101140_7e037ade06a42cef9c49ae533711f153.jpg&h=1125eabe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n油塘出現變態怪賊。現場為油美苑澤美閣停車場地下，消息稱，凌晨2時許，一名38歲姓曾女子行經上址時，突然被一名陌生男子從後箍頸揮拳襲擊，對方聲稱打劫，女事主稱沒有攜帶銀包，身上並無分文，賊人繼而扯走其胸圍及脫走其「打底褲」，隨即逃去無蹤。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171212/s00001/1513041962650\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171212%2Fs00001%2F1513041962650&d=Wk6sw9ONsJJDxQCO8jxROjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=bfe63c1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171212%2Fs00001%2F1513041962650&h=8bb7223d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171212/s00001/1513041962650</a>"},{"pid":"1e88a74de168b4373252a9f32c1991e8970c5643","tid":496664,"uid":22893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T02:13:46.000Z","msg":"操緊野，同星爺同拳館架"},{"pid":"917d9c3c24cb21f00c620ae6f1441c45727eb0ac","tid":496664,"uid":23511,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T02:28:30.000Z","msg":"小姐，閣下貌美如花， 夜闌人靜，獨自歸家，容乜易有色狼辣手摧花，扯你條底橫，撕你個Bra？"},{"pid":"f8734d5c6a4a3afff2f0e15a1a102be062e632a7","tid":496664,"uid":33756,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T02:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁呢件算係非禮